Instructions

DBT Side

1) Create a folder to save the project

2) Create virtual env --> python -m venv [venv] 
Failed: Not able to create venv with python

3) Activate the env --> .\venv\Scripts\Activate

4) Install the dbt from Snowflake --> pip install dbt-snowflake==1.10.2

5) Check if dbt was installed correctly -> dbt --version

Snowflake side

1) Create database and schema

CREATE DATABASE ventas_dw;
CREATE SCHEMA ventas_dw.staging;
CREATE SCHEMA ventas_dw.analytics;

2) Creta datawarehouse

CREATE WAREHOUSE my_wh WITH WAREHOUSE_SIZE = 'XSMALL' AUTO_SUSPEND = 60 AUTO_RESUME = TRUE;


